<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="U" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Unwillingly" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Unwillingly,</orth> against one's wish, reluctantly: <bibl n="shak. tmp 1.2.368" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. I, 2, 368</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tgv 2.1.129" default="NO" valid="yes">Gent. II, 1, 129</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mv 5.196" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. V, 196</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ayl 2.7.147" default="NO" valid="yes">As II, 7, 147</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 4.4.477" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. IV, 4, 477</bibl>. <cit><quote>I have, and most u., of late heard many grievous complaints of you,</quote> <bibl n="shak. h8 5.1.98" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 V, 1, 98</bibl></cit> (== with regret).
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>